  "title": "Better With Gold",
  "description": "this mod changes how you use gold tools, adding more items, tools and armors",
  "body": "<!-- Header Images -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d275pLd.png\" alt=\"Header 1\" style=\"margin-right:10px;\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Social Badges -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- About Header -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" alt=\"About Header\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- About Text -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\">\n  <strong>Better With Gold</strong> is a lightweight expansion mod that gives gold the value and utility it always deserved.  \n  Instead of being just shiny, now it’s <strong>powerful</strong>, <strong>versatile</strong>, and <strong>worth collecting</strong>.\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 40px auto;\">\n  Craft new <strong>gold-based armors</strong>, <strong>tools</strong>, and <strong>special items</strong> with unique traits that set them apart from vanilla gear.  \n  Perfect for solo worlds, multiplayer, or modpacks.\n</p>\n\n<!-- Ko-fi Button -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" width=\"240\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\" style=\"border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Features Header -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" alt=\"Features Header\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Gold Upgrade Templates -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#e03e2d;\">Gold Upgrade Templates</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 20px auto;\">\n  Use a <strong>Smithing Table</strong> to apply <strong>Gold Upgrade Templates</strong>, unlocking special properties for gold gear:\n</p>\n<ul style=\"max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 30px auto;\">\n  <li>Add <strong>enchantment-like effects without XP</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Combine materials</strong> to evolve your tools</li>\n  <li>Transform basic gold gear into <strong>specialized equipment</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 30px auto;\">\n  <strong>Templates can be obtained by:</strong><br>\n  - Crafting (7 Gold Ingots + 1 Amethyst + 1 Obsidian)<br>\n  - Looting dungeon/temple/vault chests<br>\n  - Trading with specialized villagers\n</p>\n\n<!-- New Weapons -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#3598db;\">New Weapons</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 20px auto;\">All weapons include both <strong>normal</strong> and <strong>reinforced</strong> variants.</p>\n\n<h3>Golden Scythe</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Executes <strong>AOE sweeping attacks</strong></li>\n  <li>Great for crowd clearing</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Great Axe</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deals <strong>more damage the lower your enemy’s health</strong> is</li>\n  <li>A brutal execution weapon</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Impact Blade</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Damage increases based on <strong>fall distance</strong></li>\n  <li>Jump attacks hit extremely <em>hard</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- New Food Item -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#e03e2d;\">New Food Item – Golden Fish</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 30px auto;\">Grants powerful effects when eaten:</p>\n<ul style=\"max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 50px auto;\">\n  <li><strong>Water Breathing</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Regeneration</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Dolphin’s Grace</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Installation Header -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" alt=\"Installation Header\">\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto 50px auto;\">\n  - <strong>Minecraft:</strong> 1.16.5 · 1.18.2 · 1.19.2 · 1.20.1 · 1.21.1 · 1.21.5 · 1.21.8<br>\n  - <strong>Loaders:</strong> Forge or NeoForge<br>\n  - <strong>Library:</strong> JAUMl\n</p>\n\n<!-- Section Divider -->\n<hr style=\"margin: 50px 0; border: none; border-top: 2px solid #ECEBE6;\">\n",
